{"tid":688970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽落正面但其實係sad既歌","createTime":"2018-06-03T16:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T00:15:07.000Z","uid":5996,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3e20f13e4573d75005de88a1641abc4fe97988bc","tid":688970,"uid":5996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:56:38.000Z","msg":"暫時諗到美麗之最同白色風車<br />\n有冇人想討論下呢兩首/ 其他同類既歌想講咩?<br />\n<br />\n白色風車個人覺得係講緊一個表白失敗既故事<br />\n就係條仔響海灘同條女表白<br />\n「複雜的眼淚」：眼淚係條仔既眼淚<br />\n「謝謝你讓我聽見」：多謝你坦白地拒絕我<br />\n「因為我在等待永遠」＝因為我在永遠等待＝因為我仲on99咁等緊你，所以先有上一句既「多謝你坦白」<br />\n<br />\n一開頭既「握著我的手」只係佢表白前幻想<br />\n但事實係「很可惜沒有祝福」<br />\n之後就係一連串條女既坦白"},{"pid":"472b27077a4e4db01f4f35d1db5b4487298484ab","tid":688970,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"我的快樂時代。"},{"pid":"ef6428a1a611b8450a85edb3e7a76ed9dfa99a5e","tid":688970,"uid":184116,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:15:57.000Z","msg":"那些你很冒險的夢"},{"pid":"66b2c3c100d03b5e65832c06511865672e1f21f8","tid":688970,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"郭富城的弱"},{"pid":"de84837df497d55126212ca00c820f728e55166e","tid":688970,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:31:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OggDVRkivs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOggDVRkivs8&d=355SayNJ4lPAGkDau7vTPwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=159cfec7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OggDVRkivs8</a>"},{"pid":"21441298e73f6e29a2a885b9541808af8bdbafb9","tid":688970,"uid":15136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:32:13.000Z","msg":"當你-林俊𠎀<br />\n旋律好輕快，但歌詞好sad"},{"pid":"cf5c962c402d02504af4fec09526d48e1b7fb6c5","tid":688970,"uid":776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76fa9a0fb7d0e89a8b8a6e22b9cd80457b742546"